<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="d59fec92-00ae-4aaf-bfef-09bc16aac76e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="aee8dca6-1c31-4667-9c4b-df092ad3bd5b">Challenge</span>&nbsp;3 (700 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="719e4207-9d00-459c-bb7a-a9b3e2425908"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2398c709-d9b4-4c44-b730-f82790a78b30">Keen Hearing and Smell.</span>&nbsp;The hound has advantage on Wisdom (<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a>) checks that rely on hearing or smell.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="8b032f6b-64bc-4633-8ecd-ce27aedd5b53"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="dcb5cbc3-59db-4869-9015-4af356f202b4">Pack Tactics.&nbsp;</span>The hound has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the hound&rsquo;s allies is within 5 feet of the creature and the ally isn&rsquo;t <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Incapacitated" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/7-tooltip">incapacitated</a>.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="356f2ef8-76cd-48af-af3b-28b7c1c1472b">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="a8d43fc0-b66f-4536-8bdb-08b7851f6c8e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="115efe58-29df-4cfc-8b4b-99a02d9405c3">Bite.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b08220d2-a317-4a30-8107-545a1f79ac37">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="f06dd947-f2a2-418c-89ab-7defbb7ddc79">Hit:&nbsp;</span>7 (1d8 + 3) piercing damage plus 7 (2d6) fire damage.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="941dca02-ac55-4d9f-899c-527e2efa4a56"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="ca9e379a-13df-428b-99d1-f429ba1f1373">Fire Breath (Recharge 5&ndash;6).&nbsp;</span>The hound exhales fire in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, taking 21 (6d6) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>
