<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="b96ad0d8-cb6e-4d1f-87a6-c942a55681ab"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6e7358a0-4aaa-462a-b71a-883c0e719fa1">Senses</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Darkvision" data-tooltip-href="/senses/2-tooltip">darkvision</a> 120 ft., passive Perception 11</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="e691c190-3a72-4ed4-92ea-31df6b5a13f0"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e4e98a5b-003d-4abf-817d-0bb64f01b2a9">Languages</span>&nbsp;Abyssal, telepathy 120 ft.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="8d13366e-c615-43ae-b991-b38df80a4e0e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e2013f18-8038-4685-88c5-60d68c4a5c87">Challenge</span>&nbsp;8 (3,900 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="e835ee6f-6a12-4575-a919-8608109cd5ae"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="08d6221f-16d6-4933-a243-f6e7e965e71a">Magic Resistance.</span>&nbsp;The hezrou has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="f1d1577e-d100-471e-a1d5-f510a8f0306e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="954a6000-0aad-4b76-98f7-3e04fb5c0a16">Stench.&nbsp;</span>Any creature that starts its turn within 10 feet of the hezrou must succeed on a DC 14 Constitution saving throw or be <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/11-tooltip">poisoned</a> until the start of its next turn. On a successful saving throw, the creature is immune to the hezrou&rsquo;s stench for 24 hours.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="86762d83-5b7d-46f8-a624-f00dd54812cf">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="70eb8645-ea3a-4192-b98b-9619a69181d1"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4cdf4999-577b-44f9-8e76-08d6ff9ebad7">Multiattack.</span>&nbsp;The hezrou makes three attacks: one with its bite and two with its claws.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="4d1c5298-696c-4994-9134-2a9c56b23fb2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="83278009-9f59-41f0-9bda-92ea5cb3eb03">Bite.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="618b2626-2a1f-4096-8acc-06a4bd5ee6ce">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+7 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="16712eb4-5e50-4847-a05e-73d743d6b4ee">Hit:&nbsp;</span>15 (2d10 + 4) piercing damage.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="7aead9b3-fbe0-4ec9-8a65-ab9429cc6cf3"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5907226f-c127-4cc3-88c6-0ee267b20ed9">Claw.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="72d2e835-36a0-4d67-85f0-b8f6a6a80d18">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+7 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="f31bb5df-3b9c-4bda-9434-72b941cccfc4">Hit:</span>&nbsp;11 (2d6 + 4) slashing damage.</p>
