<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="25ae1598-13a8-4e6e-ac29-7efa2d66d0bd">Hill giants are selfish, dimwitted brutes that hunt and raid in constant search of food. Their skins are tan from lives spent beneath the sun, and their weapons are uprooted trees and rocks pulled from the earth.</p>
