<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="9cb8f573-764f-4ef9-9b4b-9eec8ceb0b56"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="8de4ae35-894e-4e00-972b-6b3cc38f8001">Challenge</span>&nbsp;1/2 (100 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="d7a7ec8f-a473-48c1-9ad4-9a9b27b14b12"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="8e132326-6e37-4573-9df6-74a4c0b5832e">Martial Advantage.&nbsp;</span>Once per turn, the hobgoblin can deal an extra 7 (2d6) damage to a creature it hits with a weapon attack if that creature is within 5 feet of an ally of the hobgoblin that isn&rsquo;t <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Incapacitated" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/7-tooltip">incapacitated</a>.</p>
