<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="6fbb4c04-861d-4e5f-89c3-b3e60eded8d4"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="54b59d27-4d16-46d9-87c6-d8e9e183b06e">Longsword.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6e3d9853-1406-4640-b9e3-f955cfede543">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e888aa94-70cd-47ff-a571-2dc69e60231c">Hit:</span>&nbsp;5 (1d8 + 1) slashing damage, or 6 (1d10 + 1) slashing damage if used with two hands.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="84424340-5485-40fe-b86f-cfab503a9156"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="ec7a6e77-c27b-4492-a8ab-669d6c9b5955">Longbow.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="99bbe1b1-fcac-4a40-88ae-8c8f234ba2d2">Ranged Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+3 to hit, range 150/600 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="a093ab8b-7512-43d1-b2c3-1b99cffa2ad3">Hit:</span>&nbsp;5 (1d8 + 1) piercing damage.</p>
