<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="f85a671a-5f3b-4414-873e-64fa3a586bb1">Hobgoblins are large goblinoids with dark orange or red-orange skin. A hobgoblin measures virtue by physical strength and martial prowess, caring about nothing except skill and cunning in battle.</p>
<div class="Basic-Text-Frame" data-content-chunk-id="b250b549-bdd8-418f-941e-d1ef63c65859">
