<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="20446879-afe8-4550-8017-731e114b2f68"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="86830cc7-32b1-46c6-ae10-5636ed5a717a">Languages</span>&nbsp;understands the languages of its creator but can&rsquo;t speak</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="985e04fa-0431-4cf2-a160-3178b99b8eb2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="60d4038a-f4e2-478e-bf65-130ef7cce299">Challenge</span>&nbsp;0 (10 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="189308d6-4fdb-4413-8f67-aeda228c1a8c"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c5c6f413-456c-4ba9-82c6-dae09d972647">Telepathic Bond.</span>&nbsp;While the homunculus is on the same plane of existence as its master, it can magically convey what it senses to its master, and the two can communicate telepathically.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="5ab1e833-d57c-4bbc-963b-01c9183a240b">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="a6ac68c1-1f66-4c01-8e67-4bb20432a4c2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="cc0f2f21-81c8-4ce4-96d0-0a43fec53163">Bite.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="ea734c67-9e67-48a4-877e-ad52da053267">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="fb5d8d39-2afe-4782-8543-4baa1b39a260">Hit:</span>&nbsp;1 piercing damage, and the target must succeed on a DC 10 Constitution saving throw or be <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/11-tooltip">poisoned</a> for 1 minute. If the saving throw fails by 5 or more, the target is instead <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/11-tooltip">poisoned</a> for 5 (1d10) minutes and <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Unconscious" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/15-tooltip">unconscious</a> while <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/11-tooltip">poisoned</a> in this way.</p>
</div>
