<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="7c8114a4-d99a-4415-8c2e-7e17c132f657"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16927-horned-devil" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16927-tooltip">Horned Devil</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="4c93e7b4-5578-4f3a-8ef5-9f3374c77fbd">Large fiend (devil), lawful evil</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="35503bb4-1ee2-4b8b-9234-99ef5e6ef70e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1900022a-01b3-4b8d-b921-8b12480c83ff">Armor Class</span>&nbsp;18 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="0e27f715-ccee-4b91-b4b1-cacbd7613fe6"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="10f93147-f49a-4ae8-b032-b3fe9331491e">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;178 (17d10 + 85)</p>
