<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="126fb06a-f1d0-4c1d-ab70-da8cce6d0325"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="77cb3ab4-c5e7-4b40-a766-ac33a27ace91">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;5 (1d8 + 1)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="dbff9c39-3ff9-46ff-9fa2-f7980d7eee9c"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="60302719-dfd1-4f3b-9335-f860717a2229">Sp</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="026d3de1-e050-4808-b5ba-75545d78a2e0">eed</span>&nbsp;50 ft.</p>
